#: ../srcs/generated/cymel.constants.rst:28
msgid "Constants:"
msgstr "Constants:"

#: cymel.constants.AVOID_ZERO_DIV_PRECISION:1 of
msgid "Maya では scale=0 を設定しても matrix 値は 1.e-12 くらいで潰れずに保持するようなので、それを意識した極小値。"
msgstr ""
"In Maya, even if you set scale=0, the matrix value seems to be maintained at"
" around 1.e-12 without being crushed, so keep this in mind when setting the "
"minimum value."

